[06:33] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'interested in reading further, I\'ll link to this main page in the description below. Also this week, NVIDIA releases their own interactive world model. It\'s called Sana WM, and this is a super tiny'

[06:45] [scene:talk]
