AUDIO: 'them 15 days on 64 H100 GPUs to train this. Usually, it takes much longer to train a foundation model from scratch. They also made a distilled variant which can run on a single RTX 5090 with'

[07:50] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'quantization. So, this can create a minute-long clip in just 34 seconds. Now, if you scroll up to the top of the page, here it says that it will be open-sourced and the models are coming soon. For now, if you\'re interested in'

[08:03] [scene:talk]
