[12:44] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'of this as like the difference between emailing someone a problem and waiting for them to reply versus standing at a whiteboard and working something out together. The AI can jump in when it sees something, speak while listening,'

[12:56] [scene:talk]
