AUDIO: 'and translate in real time, react to visual cues, and even keep talking while a deeper background model handles longer reasoning or tool use. It\'s also time aware, so it has a built-in sense of how'

[13:09] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'much time has gone by, which enables things like reminders and mid-task prompts. So, how this works is the system actually consists of two different models. There\'s a lightweight interaction model that stays present for'

